                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.11/6966.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Special Agent <persName type="from">Silliman</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">San Luis Potosi</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-11-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">3d November 24, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department’s November 22. Los Mochis matter taken up with Foreign Secretary on
                    train prior to arrival here. He said additional telegraphic instruction for
                    proper protection would be sent from San Luis Potosi.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Silliman.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
